Subject: AD Daily Job Error
Description:
I was looking for data from an AD report regarding Weak PWs, when I found an error:
'AD/daily/user/AD_weakpasswords "Job connection profile is not available"'
Solution_Comment__c:
+++++
1) Navigate to NEA > Jobs > Active Directory > 2.Daily > 2.Users > AD_WeakPasswords
2) Right-Click the "AD_WeakPasswords" Job and select "Properties"
3) On the "Job Properties" popup, select the "Connection" tab.
4) For the "Select one of the user defined profiles", we selected the "Brazooria-Stealthbits-Collect" User Profile and clicked the "OK" button.
+++++
